(11, 'Về đâu mái tóc người thương', '<p>Hồn lỡ sa v&agrave;o đ&ocirc;i mắt em&nbsp;<br />\r\nChiều nao x&otilde;a t&oacute;c ngồi b&ecirc;n r&egrave;m&nbsp;<br />\r\nThầm ước nhưng n&agrave;o đ&acirc;u d&aacute;m&nbsp;n&oacute;i&nbsp;<br />\r\nKh&eacute;p t&acirc;m tư lại th&ocirc;i&nbsp;<br />\r\nĐường hoa vẫn chưa mở lối&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Đời lắm phong trần tay trắng tay&nbsp;<br />\r\nTrời đ&ocirc;ng ngại gi&oacute; l&ugrave;a vai gầy&nbsp;<br />\r\nLầu k&iacute;n trăng về kh&ocirc;ng lối chiếu&nbsp;<br />\r\nG&aacute;c cao ngăn niềm y&ecirc;u, th&igrave; th&ocirc;i mơ ước chi nhiều&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB&ecirc;n nhau sao t&igrave;nh xa vạn l&yacute;,&nbsp;<br />\r\nC&aacute;ch biệt mấy sơn kh&ecirc;&nbsp;<br />\r\nNg&agrave;y đi mắt em xanh biển s&acirc;u, mắt t&ocirc;i rưng rưng sầu&nbsp;<br />\r\nLặng nghe tiếng ph&aacute;o tiễn ai qua cầu&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nĐường phố mu&ocirc;n m&agrave;u sao thiếu em&nbsp;<br />\r\nVề đ&acirc;u l&agrave;n t&oacute;c x&otilde;a b&ecirc;n r&egrave;m&nbsp;<br />\r\nLầu vắng kh&ocirc;ng người song kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n&nbsp;<br />\r\nNhớ em t&ocirc;i gọi t&ecirc;n, chỉ nghe tiếng l&aacute; rơi thềm.</p>\r\n', '2019-08-10 09:05:31', 'vdmtnt-165967661774700.jpg', 6, 2),
(12, 'My love', '<p>An empty street, an empty house&nbsp;<br />\r\nA hole inside my heart&nbsp;<br />\r\nI&#39;m all alone, the rooms are getting smaller&nbsp;<br />\r\nI wonder how, I wonder why, I wonder where they are&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe days we had, the songs we sang together&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd all my love, I&#39;m holding on forever&nbsp;<br />\r\nReaching for the love that seems so far&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo I say a little prayer&nbsp;<br />\r\nAnd hope my dreams will take me there&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the skies are blue, to see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\nOver seas from coast to coast&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo find the place I love the most&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the fields are green, to see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>I try to read, I go to work&nbsp;<br />\r\nI&#39;m laughing with my friends&nbsp;<br />\r\nBut I can&#39;t stop to keep myself from thinking&nbsp;<br />\r\nI wonder how, I wonder why, I wonder where they are&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe days we had, the songs we sang together&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd all my love, I&#39;m holding on forever&nbsp;<br />\r\nReaching for the love that seems so far&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo I say a little prayer&nbsp;<br />\r\nAnd hope my dreams will take me there&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the skies are blue, to see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\nOver seas from coast to coast&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo find the place I Love The Most&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the fields are green, to see you once again&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo hold you in my arms&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo promise you my love&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo tell you from the heart&nbsp;<br />\r\nYou&#39;re all I&#39;m thinking of&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReaching for the love that seems so far&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo I say a little prayer&nbsp;<br />\r\nAnd hope my dreams will take its there&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the skies are blue, to see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\nOver seas from coast to coast&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo find the place I Love The Most&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the fields are green, to see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSay it in a prayer&nbsp;<br />\r\nDreams will take it there&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the skies are blue&nbsp;<br />\r\nto see you once again my love&nbsp;<br />\r\nOver seas from coast to coast&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo find the place I Love The Most&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhere the fields are green, to see you once again&nbsp;<br />\r\nMy Love</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-08-10 14:49:15', 'ml-166108995893553.jpg', 10, 1),
(13, 'Thần thoại', '<p>Th&agrave;nh Long:&nbsp;<br />\r\n解开我 最神秘的等待&nbsp;<br />\r\n星星坠落 风在吹动&nbsp;<br />\r\n终于再将你拥入怀中&nbsp;<br />\r\n两颗心颤抖&nbsp;<br />\r\n相信我 不变的真心&nbsp;<br />\r\n千年等待 有我承诺&nbsp;<br />\r\n无论经过多少的寒冬&nbsp;<br />\r\n我决不放手&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Kim Hee Sun :&nbsp;<br />\r\n现在紧抓住我的手 闭上眼睛&nbsp;<br />\r\n请你回想起过去我们恋爱的日子&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们是因为太爱&nbsp;<br />\r\n所以更使得我们痛苦&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们连&ldquo;爱你&rdquo;这句话都无法讲&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHiếu115 : 祝大家天天快乐~&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh&agrave;nh Long:&nbsp;<br />\r\n每一夜 被心痛穿越&nbsp;<br />\r\n思念永没有终点&nbsp;<br />\r\n早习惯了孤独相随&nbsp;<br />\r\n我微笑面对&nbsp;<br />\r\n相信我 你选择等待&nbsp;<br />\r\n再多苦痛也不闪躲&nbsp;<br />\r\n只有你的温柔能解救&nbsp;<br />\r\n无边的冷漠&nbsp;<br />\r\nKim Hee Sun :&nbsp;<br />\r\n现在紧抓住我的手 闭上眼睛&nbsp;<br />\r\n请你回想起过去我们恋爱的日子&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们是因为太爱&nbsp;<br />\r\n所以更使得我们痛苦&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们连&ldquo;爱你&rdquo;这句话都无法讲&nbsp;<br />\r\n合:&nbsp;<br />\r\n让爱成为你我心中&nbsp;<br />\r\n那永远盛开的花&nbsp;<br />\r\n穿越时空绝不低头 永不放弃的梦&nbsp;<br />\r\nKim Hee Sun :&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们是因为太爱&nbsp;<br />\r\n所以更使得我们痛苦&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们连&ldquo;爱你&rdquo;这句话都无法讲&nbsp;<br />\r\n合:&nbsp;<br />\r\n让爱成为你我心中&nbsp;<br />\r\n那永远盛开的花&nbsp;<br />\r\nKim Hee Sun :&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们千万不要忘记 我们的约定&nbsp;<br />\r\n合:&nbsp;<br />\r\n唯有真爱追随你我&nbsp;<br />\r\n穿越无尽时空&nbsp;<br />\r\nKim Hee Sun :&nbsp;<br />\r\n我们连&ldquo;爱你&rdquo;这句话都无法讲&nbsp;<br />\r\nTh&agrave;nh Long:&nbsp;<br />\r\n爱是心中唯一不变美丽的神话</p>\r\n', '2019-08-08 17:15:35', 'tt-166406488895148.jpg', 11, 6),
(14, 'Cung dưỡng tình ái', '<p>Ba ni peng zai shou shang qian cheng di fen xiang&nbsp;<br />\r\nJian xia yi duan zhu guang jiang jing lun dian liang&nbsp;<br />\r\nBu qiu dang qi hui chang zhi qiu ai yi chang&nbsp;<br />\r\nAi dao zui hou shou liao shang ku de hao jue wang&nbsp;<br />\r\nWo yong jin yi sheng yi shi lai jiang ni gong yang&nbsp;<br />\r\nzhi qi pan ni ting zhu liu zhuan di mu guang&nbsp;<br />\r\nQing ci yu wo wu xian ai yu bei ai di li liang&nbsp;<br />\r\nRang wo neng an xin zai pu di xia jing jing di guan xiang&nbsp;<br />\r\nBa ni fang zai xin shang ge qi liao shou zhang&nbsp;<br />\r\nMo mo qi qiu shang cang zhi yin wo fang xiang&nbsp;<br />\r\nBu qiu di jiu tian chang zhi qiu zai shen bang&nbsp;<br />\r\nLei liao zui dao wen rou xiang qing qing di fan chang&nbsp;<br />\r\nWo yong jin yi sheng yi shi lai jiang ni gong yang&nbsp;<br />\r\nzhi qi pan ni ting zhu liu zhuan di mu guang&nbsp;<br />\r\nQing ci yu wo wu xian ai yu bei ai di li liang&nbsp;<br />\r\nRang wo neng an xin zai pu di xia jing jing di guan xiang&nbsp;<br />\r\nWo yong jin yi sheng yi shi lai jiang ni gong yang&nbsp;<br />\r\nRen shi xian you tai duo di fan nao yao wang&nbsp;<br />\r\nKu hai zhong piao dang zhuo ni na jiu shi di mo yang&nbsp;<br />\r\nyi hui tou fa xian zao yi ta chu liao hong chen wan zhang&nbsp;<br />\r\nLa...... la...... la......&nbsp;<br />\r\nWo tai tou kan jian liao guang mang wan zhang......&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Đặt ngươi trong l&ograve;ng tay, th&agrave;nh khẩn thắp n&eacute;n hương&nbsp;<br />\r\nChỉ một ngọn nến cũng đủ thắp s&aacute;ng kinh lu&acirc;n&nbsp;<br />\r\nKh&ocirc;ng cần da diết n&atilde;o l&ograve;ng, chỉ mong được y&ecirc;u một lần&nbsp;<br />\r\nY&ecirc;u đến ph&uacute;t cuối lại bị tổn thương, kh&oacute;c trong tuyệt vọng&nbsp;<br />\r\nTa nguyện trọn đời trọn kiếp cung dưỡng ngươi&nbsp;<br />\r\nChỉ cần &aacute;nh mắt đang xoay chuyển của người dừng lại&nbsp;<br />\r\nXin h&atilde;y cho ta sức mạnh v&ocirc; hạn của y&eci